NK061(ku)001:1611: ston pa sprul pa'i sku dang ldan pa'am mdzad pa'i don bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1612: zhabs dang zhabs kyi bzhugs tshul gyi don bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1613: phyag dang phyag mtshan gyi don bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1615: dang po ston pa chos kyi sku dang ldan pa'am sku dang zhal gyi don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:1616: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal zhing zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:1617: rgyal ba drug pa la sogs pa'i sku ni rang
NK061(ku)001:1618: byung gi ye shes kho na'i phyir mdun dang rgyab
NK061(ku)001:1619: gnyis rang rgyud du grub pa med pa yin te/
NK061(ku)001:1620: de yang dbyings la thug pa med pa'i rtags su mdun rang rgyud du grub pa med/
NK061(ku)001:1621: ye shes la 'gag pa med pa'i rtags su rgyab rang rgyud du grub pa med/
NK061(ku)001:1622: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis ka'i don cis kyang ma bsgribs par gsal ba'i rtags su/
NK061(ku)001:1623: gdul bya'i snang ba la phyogs thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal zhing snang ba'o //
NK061(ku)001:1625: skabs 'dir mi mthun pa'i tshig don byung ste/
NK061(ku)001:1626: de yang mi mthun pa'i tshig don sdeb ma shes
NK061(ku)001:1627: na shes rab long ba'i bshad par 'gro ba'i skyon
NK061(ku)001:1628: spang ba'i phyir/ mi mthun pa'i tshig don sdeb pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:1629: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1630: thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal ba 'gal lo zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:1631: de'i skyon sel lugs gnyis te/
NK061(ku)001:1634: dbyings la thug pa med pa ni don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:1635: rtags de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la mdun rang rgyud pa med/
NK061(ku)001:1636: ye shes la 'gag pa med pa ni don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:1637: rtags de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la rgyab rang rgyud pa med/
NK061(ku)001:1638: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa cis kyang ma bsgribs par gsal ba don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:1639: rtags thams cad du zhal thal le ba gsal ba yin pas mi 'gal/
NK061(ku)001:1640: gnyis pa snang ba gnyis su cha phye na yang mi 'gal te/
NK061(ku)001:1641: sku mdun dang rgyab med par de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba yin la/
NK061(ku)001:1642: thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal ba ni gdul bya'i snang ba yin pas mi 'gal lo //
NK061(ku)001:1643: gtsang pa byi ston na re/
NK061(ku)001:1644: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa kas thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal ba yin la/
NK061(ku)001:1645: mdun rgyab gnyis su yod na thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal ba mi 'ong gsung /
NK061(ku)001:1646: gnyis pa ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang ldan pa'am rgyan gyi don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:1647: mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan pa/
NK061(ku)001:1649: 'di la spyir thun mong gi mtshan dpe dang /
NK061(ku)001:1650: thun mong ma yin pa mchog gi mtshan dpe gnyis las/
NK061(ku)001:1651: dang po thun mong gi mtshan dpe'i mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis ni/
NK061(ku)001:1653: phyag zhabs 'khor los mtshan dang rus sbal zhabs //
NK061(ku)001:1654: phyag dang zhabs sor d+r+wa bas 'brel ba dang //
NK061(ku)001:1655: phyag dang zhabs bcas 'jam zhing gzhon sha chags //
NK061(ku)001:1656: 'di yi sku ni bdun dag mtho ba dang //
NK061(ku)001:1657: sor mo ring dang rting yangs sku che drang //
NK061(ku)001:1658: zhabs 'bur mi mngon spu ni gyen du phyogs //
NK061(ku)001:1659: byin pa e na ya 'dra phyag ring mdzes //
NK061(ku)001:1660: 'doms kyi lba ba sbubs su nub pa'i mchog /pags pa gser mdog pags pa srab pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1661: spu ni re re nas g.yas legs 'khrungs dang //
NK061(ku)001:1662: zhal mdzod spus brgyan ro stod seng ge 'dra //
NK061(ku)001:1663: 'di yi dpung pa'i mgo zlum thal gong rgyas //
NK061(ku)001:1664: 'di la ro mi zhim pa ro mchog snang //
NK061(ku)001:1665: sku ni nya gro ta ltar chu zheng gab //
NK061(ku)001:1666: gtsug tor dbur ldan ljags ring mdzes pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1667: tshangs dbyangs 'gram pa seng ge 'dra dang tshems //
NK061(ku)001:1668: shin tu dkar dang tshad mnyam thags bzang dang //
NK061(ku)001:1669: grangs ni bzhi bcu tham pa tshang ba dang //
NK061(ku)001:1670: spyan ni mthon mthing spyan rdzi ba mchog gi //
NK061(ku)001:1671: 'dra ba 'di dag sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan //
NK061(ku)001:1673: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu ni/
NK061(ku)001:1674: thub pa'i sen mo zangs mdog dang //
NK061(ku)001:1675: mdog snum mtho dang sor mo rnams //
NK061(ku)001:1676: zlum rgyas byin gyis phra ba dang //
NK061(ku)001:1677: rtsa mi mngon dang mdud pa med //
NK061(ku)001:1678: long bu mi mngon zhabs mnyam dang //
NK061(ku)001:1679: seng ge glang chen bya dang ni //
NK061(ku)001:1680: khyu mchog stabs gshegs g.yas phyogs dang //
NK061(ku)001:1681: mdzes gshegs drang dang 'khril bag chags //
NK061(ku)001:1683: gtsang dang 'jam dang dag pa'i sku //
NK061(ku)001:1684: mtshan ni yongs su rdzogs pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1685: sku yi kho lag yangs shing bzang //
NK061(ku)001:1686: gom snyoms pa dang spyan gnyis ni //
NK061(ku)001:1687: dag dang gzhon sha can nyid dang //
NK061(ku)001:1688: sku zhum med dang rgyas par dang //
NK061(ku)001:1689: shin tu grims pa'i sku nyid dang //
NK061(ku)001:1690: yan lag shin tu rnam 'byes dang //
NK061(ku)001:1691: gzigs pa sgrib med dag pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1692: sku zlum skabs phyin ma rnyongs dang //
NK061(ku)001:1693: phyang nge ba dang lte ba ni //
NK061(ku)001:1694: zab dang g.yas phyogs 'khyil ba dang //
NK061(ku)001:1695: kun nas lta na sdug pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1696: sku spyod gtsang dang sku la ni //
NK061(ku)001:1697: sme ba gnag bag med pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1698: phyag ni shing bal ltar 'jam dang //
NK061(ku)001:1699: phyag ring mdangs yod zab ring dang //
NK061(ku)001:1700: zhal ni ha cang mi ring dang //
NK061(ku)001:1701: mchu ni bim pa ltar dmar dang //
NK061(ku)001:1702: ljags mnyen pa dang srab pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1703: dmar dang 'brug gi sgra nyid dang //
NK061(ku)001:1704: gsung snyan 'jam dang mche ba ni //
NK061(ku)001:1705: rno dang dkar dang mnyam pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1706: byin gyis phra dang shangs mtho dang //
NK061(ku)001:1707: mchog tu dag pa nyid dang ni //
NK061(ku)001:1708: spyan yangs pa dang rdzi ma stug /pad+ma'i 'dab ma 'dra ba dang //
NK061(ku)001:1709: smin tshugs ring dang 'jam pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1710: snum dang spu ni mnyam pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1711: phyag ring rgyas dang snyan mnyam dang //
NK061(ku)001:1712: nyams pa rnam par spangs pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1713: dpral ba legs par 'byes pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1714: dbyes che ba dang dbu rgyas dang //
NK061(ku)001:1715: dbu skra bung ba ltar gnag dang //
NK061(ku)001:1717: mi gshor dri zhim skyes bu yi //
NK061(ku)001:1718: yid ni 'phrog par byed pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:1719: dpal gyi be'u bkra shis ni //
NK061(ku)001:1720: sangs rgyas dpe byad bzang por bzhed //
NK061(ku)001:1722: 'di rnams la thun mong gi mtshan dper 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ni/
NK061(ku)001:1723: sangs rgyas longs sku dang sprul sku dang /
NK061(ku)001:1724: stong 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po la sogs pa la'ang yod pa'i phyir thun mong gi mtshan dpe ste/
NK061(ku)001:1725: 'o na de rnams la khyad par med dam zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:1726: rin po che'i phreng ba las/
NK061(ku)001:1727: 'khor lo sgyur ba thams cad la //
NK061(ku)001:1729: dag dang mdzes dang gsal ba ni //
NK061(ku)001:1730: sangs rgyas rnams kyi char mi phod //
NK061(ku)001:1732: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa mchog gi mtshan dpe la phyi nang gsang ba gsum ste/
NK061(ku)001:1733: phyi'i mtshan dpe ni lha la rtsi ba ste/
NK061(ku)001:1734: drug pa kun tu bzang po'i thugs rig pa rang
NK061(ku)001:1735: byung gi ye shes thabs kyi snang cha las sems
NK061(ku)001:1736: dpa' bcu drug /dbyings rnam par dag pa shes rab
NK061(ku)001:1737: kyi snang cha las sems ma bcu drug ste/
NK061(ku)001:1738: de ltar sum cu rtsa gnyis ni mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK061(ku)001:1739: 'o na phyi nang gi sems dpa' yab yum bcu
NK061(ku)001:1740: drug tu bshad pa la so gnyis ji ltar 'byung
NK061(ku)001:1741: snyam na/ rgyu skal bzang gi sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug dang /
NK061(ku)001:1742: 'bras bu dpe bral gyi sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug ste sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK061(ku)001:1743: de ltar 'bras bu'i sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug
NK061(ku)001:1744: po re re la yang dbu rgyan rigs kyi lha
NK061(ku)001:1745: lnga lnga dang ldan pa ni dpe byad bzang po
NK061(ku)001:1746: brgyad cu'o // de yang 'grel chung las/
NK061(ku)001:1747: sems dpa' sems mar yang dag ldan //
NK061(ku)001:1748: bcu drug rgyas btab dpe byad dang //
NK061(ku)001:1751: mtshan gyi me tog la dpe byad kyi 'bras bus
NK061(ku)001:1752: spras pa'i phyir sras kyi tshogs kyis kun nas brgyan
NK061(ku)001:1754: 'di nyid kyi le'u drug pa las //
NK061(ku)001:1755: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK061(ku)001:1756: spyod yul kun tu man+da la //
NK061(ku)001:1758: 'o na de ltar sems dpa' sems ma sum cu
NK061(ku)001:1759: rtsa gnyis po de 'khor du 'dug pa la rgyan
NK061(ku)001:1761: rgyan gyi don ni mdzes par byed pa yin la/
NK061(ku)001:1762: 'dir longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mdzes par byed pa sems dpa'/
NK061(ku)001:1763: sems dpa' mdzes par byed pa dbu rgyan te/
NK061(ku)001:1764: dper na slob dpon mdzes par byed pa grwa pa/
NK061(ku)001:1765: grwa pa mdzes par byed pa thang zhu lta bu yin zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:1766: nang gi mtshan dpe ni 'khor lo bzhi'i rtsa gnas la rtsi ste/
NK061(ku)001:1767: spyi bo bde ba chen po'i 'khor lo la rtsa
NK061(ku)001:1768: 'dab sum cu rtsa gnyis yod pa ni mtshan sum
NK061(ku)001:1770: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo la rtsa 'dab
NK061(ku)001:1771: bcu drug /snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo la rtsa
NK061(ku)001:1772: ba'i rtsa 'dab bzhi/ lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo
NK061(ku)001:1773: la rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi'i bzhi nas rlung
NK061(ku)001:1774: mi rgyu bas ma bgrangs pas brgyad cu ni dpe
NK061(ku)001:1775: ba'i rtsa 'dab bzhi/ byad brgyad cu'o // de yang thal rgyud las/
NK061(ku)001:1776: sgra dbyangs gsung gi gnas bzhi yi //
NK061(ku)001:1777: dbye bas gsum gsum ngos gnyis dang //
NK061(ku)001:1778: bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur pa yin //
NK061(ku)001:1781: yab yum gyi dga' ba la rtsi ste/
NK061(ku)001:1782: ston pa yab yum gnyis rol pa'i dus su/
NK061(ku)001:1783: yab la dga' ba bcu drug rim gyis skye/
NK061(ku)001:1784: yum la dga' ba bcu drug cig car du skye ba ni mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK061(ku)001:1785: 'o na dga' bzhir gsungs pa la bcu drug tu ji ltar 'gyur zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:1790: dga' ba'i lhan cig skyes dga' la sogs pa dga'
NK061(ku)001:1791: ba re re la'ang bzhi bzhi ste bcu drug tu
NK061(ku)001:1792: bzhed do // yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug po
NK061(ku)001:1793: re rela'ang ye shes lnga lnga'i bde ba dang ldan
NK061(ku)001:1794: pa ni dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu'o //
NK061(ku)001:1796: +aa li k+aa li'i bde ba nyid //
NK061(ku)001:1797: phan tshun ma 'dres gcig par shes //
NK061(ku)001:1798: bcu drug ngos gnyis mtshan dang ldan //
NK061(ku)001:1799: phyogs gcig ye shes lnga ldan pa //
NK061(ku)001:1800: brgyad cu'o bzod sogs rgyu las 'phags //
NK061(ku)001:1803: dus gcig ro mnyam thig le che //
NK061(ku)001:1804: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan rdzogs shing //
NK061(ku)001:1805: zla ba'i ye shes lnga bcu drug /dpe byad la sogs dpag tu med //
NK061(ku)001:1807: 'o na nang dang gsang ba'i mtshan dpe rtsa dang
NK061(ku)001:1808: khams kyi rang bzhin du 'dug pa la rgyan du
NK061(ku)001:1809: ci 'gyur zhe na/ longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la
NK061(ku)001:1810: rtsa khams rnam par dag pa bde ba chen po'i
NK061(ku)001:1811: rang bzhin du ro mnyam pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:1812: mdzes pa'i nang nas mdzes pa chen po ste/
NK061(ku)001:1813: rgyan gyi nang nas mchog yin zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:1814: de ltar phyi nang gsang ba'i mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK061(ku)001:1815: dpe byad brgyad cu ste de dag tu ldan pa ni ston pa drug pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1816: 'chad pa'i skyes bu kho na las gzhan la mi
NK061(ku)001:1817: mnga' ba'i phyir thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dape'o
NK061(ku)001:1818: // gsum pa ston pa sprul pa'i sku dang ldan pa'am mdzad pa'i don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:1819: bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba/
NK061(ku)001:1821: zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du/
NK061(ku)001:1822: sku lnga la sogs pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1823: gsung theg pa rim pa dgu dang /
NK061(ku)001:1824: thugs mkhyen pa'i ye shes tshad med pa/
NK061(ku)001:1825: ma nges sna tshogs bar dus dang gnas skabs kun tu gdul bya'i ngo la snang ba'o //
NK061(ku)001:1826: zhabs kyi bzhugs tshul 'di'i skabs su/
NK061(ku)001:1827: bla ma lce ston sgrub pa'i gsung gis/
NK061(ku)001:1828: spyir ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyi sku lnga yin te/
NK061(ku)001:1829: gong ma gsum po'ang sku gsum sbyar 'dug pas/
NK061(ku)001:1830: phyag zhabs gnyis la'ang sku sbyar ba 'thad gsungs te/
NK061(ku)001:1831: ston pa dbyer med rdo rje'i sku dang ldan pa'am
NK061(ku)001:1832: zhabs dang zhabs kyi bzhugs tshul gyi don bstan pa
NK061(ku)001:1833: ni/ thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa/
NK061(ku)001:1836: ming bzhi ldan pa'i skyil krung gnas //
NK061(ku)001:1837: zhes pas skyil krung bzhir bshad de/
NK061(ku)001:1838: thabs yab bam zhabs g.yas pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1839: shes rab kyi ste yum mam zhabs g.yon pa/
NK061(ku)001:1840: yab yum gyi rdo rje dang pad+ma gnyis rtse mo
NK061(ku)001:1841: sprad pa'i bde ba la rgyu 'bras ril mnyam par
NK061(ku)001:1842: rdzogs pa'i phyir/ 'bras bu'i ming rgyu la btags pa ste mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:1844: thabs yab dang shes rab yum gyi zhabs gnyis bsgrub
NK061(ku)001:1845: bya'i ming sgrub byed la btags nas sbyor ba'i skyil
NK061(ku)001:1846: mo la mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs zhes brjod de/
NK061(ku)001:1847: de ltar bzhugs pa ni bzhugs tshul lo //
NK061(ku)001:1849: ston pa yab yum mnyam par bzhag pa la/
NK061(ku)001:1850: bdag gzhan gyi mdzad pa thams cad rdzogs pa'i phyir rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:1851: zhabs mthil gnyis barla steng du ston pa rdo rje'i lte ba'i tshul du byas shing /
NK061(ku)001:1852: sor mo bcu rdo rje'i rwa'i tshul du byas pa ni rdo rje'i skyil mo krung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:1853: bde ba chen po'i spyod pas 'dul ba'i phyir/
NK061(ku)001:1854: bya ba ma yin pa brtul nas bya ba la
NK061(ku)001:1855: zhugs pa ni brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung du
NK061(ku)001:1857: bstan pa'i mnga' bdag 'jam pa'i dbyangs chen po'i gsung gis/
NK061(ku)001:1858: thabs yab kyi zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1859: de la shes rab yum gyi zhabs gnyis brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung du 'khyud pas/
NK061(ku)001:1860: rdo rje dang pad+ma rtsa sprad pa'i bde ba la rgyu 'bras ril mnyam par rdzogs pa'i phyir/
NK061(ku)001:1861: bde ba chen po'i ngang las mi 'gyur bar bzhugs pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:1863: lnga pa ston pa mngon byang rig pa'i sku dang
NK061(ku)001:1864: ldan pa'am phyag dang phyag mtshan gyi don bstan pa
NK061(ku)001:1865: ni/ ye shes drug gi phyag ye shes rin po che'i phyag rgya 'bar ba can/
NK061(ku)001:1867: ye shes lnga rang byung gi ye shes dang drug
NK061(ku)001:1868: gi don rgyal ba drug pa nyid la ldan pa'i
NK061(ku)001:1870: ye shes drug gi gdul bya'i don ma 'gags par
NK061(ku)001:1871: mdzad pa'i rtags su ye shes rin po che'i phyag
NK061(ku)001:1872: rgya'i dbyibs ni/ phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu/
NK061(ku)001:1873: bar pa gnyis 'khor lo dang rin po che/
NK061(ku)001:1874: tha ma gnyis pad+ma dang ral gri rigs kyi kha dog 'od 'bar ba can 'dzin pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:1876: ye shes drug phyag gi don du yang byung la/
NK061(ku)001:1877: phyag mtshan gyi don du yang byung bas ldabs so zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:1878: phyag gi ye shes drug ni ye nas gnas pa'i cha nas bzhag la/
NK061(ku)001:1879: phyag mtshan gyi ye shes drug ni/
NK061(ku)001:1880: des gdul bya'i don mdzad pa'i cha nas bzhag pas ldabs pa'i skyon med do //
NK061(ku)001:1881: drug pa dbu'i don bstan pa 'di la'ang /
NK061(ku)001:1882: yongs 'dzin chen po sh+aakya 'phel ba'i gsung gis sku sbyar ba 'thad gsung ste/
NK061(ku)001:1883: des na zur thams cad mkhyen pa chos rje chen po nyid kyi bzhed kyis/
NK061(ku)001:1884: ston pa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi sku dang ldan pa'am/
NK061(ku)001:1886: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dbu gsum dang ldan pa zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:1887: stong pa nyid rnam par thar pa'am sku bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad pa'i rtags su/
NK061(ku)001:1888: g.yas kyi dbu dkar ba nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa dang ldan pa/
NK061(ku)001:1889: smon pa med pa nyid rnam pa thar pa'am gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad pa'i rtags su/
NK061(ku)001:1890: g.yon gyii dbu dmar ba gdul bya'i don la chags pa mtshon pa dang ldan pa/
NK061(ku)001:1891: mtshan ma rnam par thar pa dang ldan pa'am thugs
NK061(ku)001:1892: bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad pa'i rtags su
NK061(ku)001:1893: dbus kyi dbu mthing kha chos nyid mi 'gyur ba
NK061(ku)001:1894: mtshon pa ste/ de ltar dbu gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:1895: 'di la bstan pa'i mnga' bdag 'jam dbyangs chen po bsam grub rdo rje'i gsung gis/
NK061(ku)001:1896: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad pa'i rtags su dbu gsum dang ldan pa/
NK061(ku)001:1897: zhes bshad na don 'dus gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:1899: dbu bsam gyis mi khyab na dbu gsum du grangs nges pa 'gal zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:1900: don du mi 'gal rtags su mi 'gal/
NK061(ku)001:1901: snang ba gnyis su cha phye nas kyang mi 'gal te/
NK061(ku)001:1902: don rtags mi 'gal ba ni bshad ma thag pa'i 'bru snon pa'i skabs kyis shes la/
NK061(ku)001:1903: snang ba gnyis su cha phye na/
NK061(ku)001:1904: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba yin la/
NK061(ku)001:1905: dbu gsum gdul bya'i snang ba yin pas mi 'gal gsung /
NK061(ku)001:1906: yang spyi dang bye brag gi phye na/
NK061(ku)001:1907: g.yas kyi dbu yang bsam gyis mi khyab/
NK061(ku)001:1908: g.yon gyi dbu yang bsam gyis mi khyab/
NK061(ku)001:1909: dbus kyi dbu yang bsam gyis mi khyab pa ste/
NK061(ku)001:1910: tshoms su bsdu na gsum yin pas mi 'gal zhing /
NK061(ku)001:1913: bar ru bzhi la dmag mang po yod kyang ru bzhi'i dmag ces/
NK061(ku)001:1914: tshoms su bsdus pa lta bu'o //
NK061(ku)001:1915: de ltar ston pa'i rang bzhin dang ngo bo gnyis
NK061(ku)001:1916: po des gang gis gsungs pa'i ston pa phun sum
NK061(ku)001:1917: tshogs pa rgyas par bstan pa yin te/
NK061(ku)001:1919: ye shes rgya mtsho 'og min gyi //
NK061(ku)001:1921: bdag po kun bzang 'khor lo bskor //
NK061(ku)001:1922: bka' sdod skyes bu mdun na gnas //
NK061(ku)001:1923: brjod pa med bzhin go bar mdzad //
NK061(ku)001:1924: dpag med ye shes yongs rdzogs pas //
NK061(ku)001:1925: zhing 'khor longs spyod phun sum ldan //
NK061(ku)001:1929: bdag po kun bzang 'khor rnams la //
NK061(ku)001:1931: mi bskyod rgyal po mdun na gnas //
NK061(ku)001:1933: rgyud kyi ston pa rigs thams cad kyi bdag po rgyal ba drug pa kun tu bzang po yin la/
NK061(ku)001:1934: 'chad pa'i skyes bu spyir rigs lnga char yin te/
NK061(ku)001:1936: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga ste //
NK061(ku)001:1939: rgyud kyi ston pa drug pa kun tu bzang po ni 'khor lo'i lte ba bzhugs la/
NK061(ku)001:1940: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rdo rje sems dpa' mdun na gnas pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:1941: spyi don gnyis pa gang du gsungs pa'i gnas phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bstan pa la lnga ste/
NK061(ku)001:1942: gnas kyi rang bzhin nam gzhi'i 'og min gsum gyi don bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1943: ngo bo'i don bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1945: rta babs kyi don bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1947: dang po gnas kyi rang bzhin nam gzhi'i 'og min gsum gyi don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:1948: 'og min gyi rgya phyogs bcur phyi dang nang zhes pa der gda' zhing /
NK061(ku)001:1949: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa na/
NK061(ku)001:1951: spyir gyi 'og min gyi zhes pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:1952: gong gang gis kyang ma chod pa'i gnas yin la/
NK061(ku)001:1953: mtha' dang dbus med pa na zhes pas rgyal ba'i
NK061(ku)001:1954: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes la mtha' dbus dang
NK061(ku)001:1956: rtags 'og min gyi gnas la yang mtha' dang dbus med pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:1957: na zhes pa ni rten pa'i tshig gi 'phrad do //
NK061(ku)001:1958: de'i shugs la 'og min bdun yang 'chad de/
NK061(ku)001:1959: rgyal ba'i thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi gong
NK061(ku)001:1960: gang gis kyang ma chod pa ni rig pa'i 'og
NK061(ku)001:1961: min/ don chos nyid kyi gong gang gis kyang gcod pa ni don gyi 'og min/
NK061(ku)001:1962: lha rtog dbyer med kyi gong gang gis kyang ma chod pa ni rtogs pa'i 'og min/
NK061(ku)001:1963: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang la bde ba skye ba'i
NK061(ku)001:1964: gong gang gis kyang ma chod pa ni gsang ba'i
NK061(ku)001:1965: 'og min/ yod min med min gyi skye mched ni bgrangs pa'i 'og min/
NK061(ku)001:1966: gzugs khams kun gyi gong na gnas pa'i 'og min ni 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min/
NK061(ku)001:1967: 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min de las nyis 'gyur
NK061(ku)001:1968: gyis spags pa na yod pa'i dus gsum gyi sangs
NK061(ku)001:1969: rgyas kun gyi bzhugs gnas su gyur cing grags pa
NK061(ku)001:1970: ni/ longs spyod chen po'i 'og min te ma spangs rgyan tshogs kyi gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK061(ku)001:1971: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa zhes pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:1972: don chos nyid la rgya chad med pa'i rtags su
NK061(ku)001:1973: gzhal yas khang la yang rgya phyogs bcur yongs su
NK061(ku)001:1974: ma chad pa'o // 'dir bla ma gtsang ba byi ston gyi gsung gis/
NK061(ku)001:1975: ngo bo snang stong dbyer med pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:1976: rtags pany+tsa re kha'i rtsig pa sna zlum pa ma yin pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:1978: phyi dang nang med pa kun tu yang nang du gyur pa na zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:1979: rgyal ba'i thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes la/
NK061(ku)001:1980: phyi gzung ba'i yul dang nang 'dzin pa'i sems nyid
NK061(ku)001:1981: rang rgyud du grub pa med pa ni don yin
NK061(ku)001:1982: la/ rtags gzhal yas khang la'ang phyi dang nang gnyis rang rgyud du grub pa med pa ste/
NK061(ku)001:1983: phyi nas bltas na nang gsal nang nas bltas na
NK061(ku)001:1984: phyi gsal zhing chos thams cad rig pa rang byung
NK061(ku)001:1985: gi ye shes 'ba' zhig tu gyur bas/
NK061(ku)001:1986: kun tu yang nang du gyur pa'i gzhal yas khang de na zhes bya'o //
NK061(ku)001:1987: 'di'i skabs su kha cig na re/
NK061(ku)001:1989: kun tu yang nang du gyur pa 'gal lo zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:1992: don ni rgyal ba'i thugs la phyi yul dang nang
NK061(ku)001:1993: sems gnyis su grub pa med pas phyi nang med
NK061(ku)001:1994: la/ sems nyid 'ba' zhig tu gyur pas nang du gyur pa zhes bya'o //
NK061(ku)001:1995: rtags ni gzhal yas khang la phyi nang med de/
NK061(ku)001:1996: gang nas bltas kyang gsal ba 'ba' zhig tu gyur pa zhes bya ste/
NK061(ku)001:1998: yang rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa zhes pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:1999: yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa zhes pa 'gal te/
NK061(ku)001:2001: nar mo gru gsum zlum po las rgya chad pas 'gal zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2005: rgyal ba'i thugs rig pa snang stong gi rgya gar yang ma chad pa yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2006: gru bzhi ni rgyal ba'i thugs la che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2007: rtags su ni gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs gru bzhir yod la/
NK061(ku)001:2008: rgya 'di tshod cig bya ba med de/
NK061(ku)001:2009: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2010: rje drings pa nye'u ston chos kyi seng ge na re/
NK061(ku)001:2011: rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2012: pany+tsa re kha'i rtsig pa sna zlum pa med de/
NK061(ku)001:2013: khor ra dang khor yug tu byung ba yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2014: gru bzhi ni gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs gru bzhir yod pa yin pas 'gal ba med gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:2016: gru bzhi nyid rgya ma chad pa yin gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:2017: gnyis pa gnas kyi ngo bo la bdun te/
NK061(ku)001:2020: dbyibs kyi don bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2021: glo 'bur gyi don bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2022: rtse mo'i don bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2023: rgyan gyi don bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2024: 'og gzhi 'bur 'phangs dang bcas pa'i don bstan pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2025: dang po 'og gzhi'i don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2026: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba la/
NK061(ku)001:2028: 'og gzhi gdul bya'i blos tshad gzung du med pa'i phyir na gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK061(ku)001:2029: de yang ye shes lnga dang ldan pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2030: de mtshon byed kyi rtags kyang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK061(ku)001:2031: dbus kyi lte ba dang lnga phan tshun rang bzhin
NK061(ku)001:2032: gyis gsal ba de la yon tan thams cad ma
NK061(ku)001:2033: btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2034: gnyis pa rgyu'i don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2035: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK061(ku)001:2037: 'o na gzhal yas khang de'i rgyu rang ci snyam na/
NK061(ku)001:2038: ye shes nyid dbyibs dang kha dog tu rang snang ba yin te/
NK061(ku)001:2039: de nyid kyi phrin las kyi gdul bya'i dgos pa skong ba don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2040: rtags rin po che 'od 'bar ba'i rgyu las grub pa blos gzhal ba las yas pa'i khang pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2041: gsum pa dbyibs kyi don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2042: yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa/
NK061(ku)001:2044: 'bras bu'i chos la che ba'i yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2045: rtags gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs gru bzhir gyur pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2046: bzhi pa glo 'bur gyi don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2047: lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa/
NK061(ku)001:2049: ye shes re re yang lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2050: rtags rtsa rgyud 'di nyid kyi dbang du lha med
NK061(ku)001:2051: kyi khang pa bzhi rigs bzhi'i kha dog can gyi
NK061(ku)001:2052: rin po che'i glo 'bur gyi gzhal yas khang gi
NK061(ku)001:2053: phyogs bzhi nas mkhar thabs su mdzes pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2054: lnga pa rtse mo'i don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2055: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i kun tu 'khyil ba/
NK061(ku)001:2057: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK061(ku)001:2058: dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad kyi rgyud dam
NK061(ku)001:2059: dgongs pa rang rig par so so ma yin pas/
NK061(ku)001:2060: ngo bo nyid du gcig pa'i ye shes las ma g.yos pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2061: rtags gzhal yas khang gi rtse mo kun tu zlum por 'khyil ba ste/
NK061(ku)001:2062: dper na sbra'am gur lta bu'o //
NK061(ku)001:2063: drug pa rgyan gyi don bstan pa la gnyis/
NK061(ku)001:2064: rin po che'i rgyan bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2066: dang po rin po che'i rgyan bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2067: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa khyad par du gyur pa/
NK061(ku)001:2068: ye shes rin po che shar bu'i rgyan dang /
NK061(ku)001:2070: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab
NK061(ku)001:2071: pa nyid cir yang mi 'gag pa'i rtsal sna tshogs
NK061(ku)001:2073: rtags gdul bya'i snang ngor ye shes rin po che'i
NK061(ku)001:2074: rgyan gyi dbyibs dang kha dog sna tshogs pa la
NK061(ku)001:2075: sogs pa'i sogs khong nas 'od zer sprul pa'i 'phro
NK061(ku)001:2076: 'du rnam pa tha dad pa'i bye brag du ma
NK061(ku)001:2077: dang ldan pa'o // de yang khyad par du gyur pa ste/
NK061(ku)001:2078: gang khyad par du gyur na/
NK061(ku)001:2079: ye shes rang snang gi rgyan de dag /gang las khyad par du gyur na/
NK061(ku)001:2081: tshul gang gis khyad par du gyur na gsum ste/
NK061(ku)001:2082: 'jig rten pa'i rgyan rnams ni lta bas ngoms la/
NK061(ku)001:2083: ye shes rang snang gi rgyan rnams ni lta bas mi ngoms shing chog mi shes pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2084: 'jig rten pa'i rgyan ni re re yang du mar mi 'char la/
NK061(ku)001:2085: ye shes rang snang gi rgyan ni re re yang du mar 'char ba dang /
NK061(ku)001:2086: 'jig rten pa'i rgyan ni gcig gis gcig sgrib la/
NK061(ku)001:2087: ye shes rang snang gi rgyan ni gcig gis gcig ma bsgribs par gsal bas na/
NK061(ku)001:2088: 'jig rten pa'i rgyan las khyad par du gyur pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2089: de yang ye shes rin po che sna tshogs kyi
NK061(ku)001:2090: dbyibs dang kha dog thugs rje dang sprul pa'i 'phro
NK061(ku)001:2091: 'du rgyun mi 'chad pa dang ldan pa don yin
NK061(ku)001:2092: la/ rtags rin po che sna tshogs kyi rgyu las grub pa'i phreng ba'i rgyan dang/
NK061(ku)001:2093: bden pa gnyis su med pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2094: rtags rin po che'i chun 'phyang gi rgyan dang /
NK061(ku)001:2095: thabs ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2096: rtags rin po che'i shar bu'i rgyan dang ldan pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2097: gnyis pa 'dod yon gyi rgyan bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2098: gzugs sna tshogs phyogs bcur 'khrigs par rang byung la/
NK061(ku)001:2099: mi sgrib par gsal ba'i rgyan bsam gyis mi khyab pas bklubs pa/
NK061(ku)001:2101: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ma spangs rnam dag rgyan du rdzogs pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2102: rtags gzugs kyi lha mo dkar mo me long bsnams pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2103: sgra'i lha mo dmar mo pi wang thogs pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2104: dri'i lha mo sngon mo dung chos thogs pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2105: ro'i lha mo ser mo mkhar gzhong g.yos kyis bkang ba thogs pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2106: reg bya'i lha mo dkar mo lha'i na bza' pany+tsa
NK061(ku)001:2107: li ka thogs pa sna tshogs kyis rang bzhin grub
NK061(ku)001:2108: pa'i dbang du phyogs bcu nas 'khrigs par rgyu rkyen
NK061(ku)001:2109: med par rang byung nas mchod pa 'bul la/
NK061(ku)001:2110: sbyor ba bsgom pa'i dbang du ni/
NK061(ku)001:2114: steng gi bya 'dabs kyi 'og /ka thung bcu drug
NK061(ku)001:2115: gi phrag /d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed kyi gseb nas mchod
NK061(ku)001:2117: de yang phyis nang mi sgrib nang gis phyi mi sgrib par gsal ba'i dpe ni/
NK061(ku)001:2118: rin po che'i gser gyi sbu gur rin po che'i ze'u kha bcug pa lta bu'am/
NK061(ku)001:2119: rin po che'i shel gyi sbu gur rin po che
NK061(ku)001:2120: sna tshogs bcug pa ltar gsal ba'i rgyan mang ba'i
NK061(ku)001:2121: tshad bsam gyis mi khyab pas zum chags pa ltar
NK061(ku)001:2122: bklubs pa'o // bdun pa 'og gzhi 'bur 'phangs kyi don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2126: theg pa gzhan las 'dir bla na med pa'i theg pa 'phar ba don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2127: rtags gzhal yang gi 'og gzhi rim pa bzhin/
NK061(ku)001:2128: rdo rje 'greng bu res spags pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2129: chos kyi dbyings la mthar thug pa med pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2130: rtags su gzhal yas khang gi bum pa'i mtho dman gyi tshad dpag tu med pa ste/
NK061(ku)001:2131: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dbu'i gtsur tor lta bu'o //
NK061(ku)001:2132: gsum pa sgo'i don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2133: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i sgo khyud can zhes pa/
NK061(ku)001:2134: gzung 'dzin las rnam par thar par byed pa'i stong
NK061(ku)001:2135: pa nyid dang mtshan ma med pa dang smon pa
NK061(ku)001:2136: med pa dang 'od gsal ba ste/
NK061(ku)001:2138: ma h+aa a tir 'jug pa'i tshul ni don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2139: rtags gzhal yas khang gi phyogs bzhir sgo bzhi ni/
NK061(ku)001:2140: thang sgo lta bu ma yin te/
NK061(ku)001:2141: 'bur sgo sgo khyud sgo rgyan dang ldan pa can no //
NK061(ku)001:2143: lam spyi'i 'jug tshul sems lnga ru/
NK061(ku)001:2146: khog gzhung rnams kyi bshad pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2147: 'dir rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi nas 'jug par bshad pa 'gal lo zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2148: thun mong pa'am spyii'i 'jug tshul sems lnga yin yang /
NK061(ku)001:2149: khyad par ram lta ba rtogs nas 'jug tshul rnam thar bzhi yin par mi 'gal te/
NK061(ku)001:2150: de yang 'di nyid kyi le'u lnga pa las/
NK061(ku)001:2151: dngos rnams nyid ni dngos med par //
NK061(ku)001:2152: rtogs pa'i dbang sgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK061(ku)001:2154: bzhi pa rta babs kyi don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2155: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta babs dang ldan pa/
NK061(ku)001:2157: 'khor ba las rnam par thar par byed pa'i theg
NK061(ku)001:2158: pa brgyad kyi lam nas bgrod pa ni don yin
NK061(ku)001:2159: la/ rtags gzhal yas khang gi sgo la phyi'i them skam bzhi nang gi them skas bzhi ste/
NK061(ku)001:2160: rgyu'i rta babs brgyad dang ldan pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2161: yang 'khor ba las rnam par thar par byed pa'i
NK061(ku)001:2162: theg pa brgyad kyi rang sa'i 'bras bu brgyad thob
NK061(ku)001:2165: rta rkang chu skyes pha gu sgrom //
NK061(ku)001:2166: sna 'phyong seng mgo shar bu phreng //
NK061(ku)001:2167: zhes rgyan gyi rta babs brgyad dang ldan pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2169: theg pa a nu man chad brgyad bgrod nas/
NK061(ku)001:2170: thob bya gsang ba'i snying por 'dod pa 'gal lo zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2173: ma h+aa man chad brgyad bgrod nas/
NK061(ku)001:2174: 'bras bu gsang ba'i snying po la sbyar ba'ang yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2175: theg pa kun gyi thob bya rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying por yin te/
NK061(ku)001:2176: 'di nyid kyi le'u tha ma las/
NK061(ku)001:2177: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK061(ku)001:2178: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK061(ku)001:2180: 'khor lo bskor ba de dag gi 'bras bu'i mchog /ces gsungs so //
NK061(ku)001:2181: lnga pa gdan khri'i don bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2182: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri rin po che'i gdan la/
NK061(ku)001:2184: 'di la'ang 'og gzhi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan dang /
NK061(ku)001:2185: smon lam gus pa'i gdan dang /
NK061(ku)001:2186: yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan dang /
NK061(ku)001:2187: sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan dang /
NK061(ku)001:2188: thugs rig pa rang snang gi gdan dang lnga las/
NK061(ku)001:2189: dang po 'og gzhi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan ni/
NK061(ku)001:2190: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dbus kyi lte ba dang bcas pa yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2191: gnyis pa smon lam gus pa'i gdan ni/
NK061(ku)001:2192: de dag gi steng dus mtha'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK061(ku)001:2193: smon lam gyi dbang gis seng ge la sogs par
NK061(ku)001:2194: sprul pa'i lus gdan du phul nas nyon mongs pa'i
NK061(ku)001:2195: sgrib pa sbyong / rna bas chos nyan nas shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyong ste/
NK061(ku)001:2197: byang chub sems dpa' smon lam dbang //
NK061(ku)001:2198: thos pa rgya mtsho bsags pa'i phyir //
NK061(ku)001:2199: lus ni seng ge'i gdan du phul //
NK061(ku)001:2202: seng ge la sogs pa smon lam gyi byang chub sems dpa' gcig kyang brgyad brgyad do //
NK061(ku)001:2204: gsum pa yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan ni/
NK061(ku)001:2205: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2206: bzhi pa sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan ni/
NK061(ku)001:2207: de rnams kyang rin po che'i khri rkang gis bteg pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2208: de dag ni rgyu'i theg pa'am rgyud mas sbyangs kyi dbang du yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2209: 'bras bu'i theg pa'am yas sprul gyi dbang du/
NK061(ku)001:2210: gdan thams cad kyang thugs rig pa rang snang gi gdan du gsungs te/
NK061(ku)001:2212: byang chub sems dpa' lus gdan du phul nas chos nyan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2213: 'bras bu'i theg pa'i skabs su 'thad par ma gsungs so //
NK061(ku)001:2214: thun mong gi dbang du'o zhes so //
NK061(ku)001:2215: de'i phyir gdan lnga ga yang thugs rig pa rang snang gi gdan gyi dbang du byas na/
NK061(ku)001:2216: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang /
NK061(ku)001:2217: zhes pas bshad ma thag pa'i gzhal yas khang de na/
NK061(ku)001:2218: rgyal ba drug pa'i thugs la mi 'jigs pa bzhi lhun gyis grub pa ni don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2219: rtags seng ge khyi tshugs pa brgyad mjug ma nang
NK061(ku)001:2220: du bsnol nas rin po che'i khri 'degs pa dang
NK061(ku)001:2221: / de yang don de bzhin gshegs pa'i mii 'jigs pa bzhi gang zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2223: mngon sangs rgyas dang zag pa zad //
NK061(ku)001:2224: bar mi chod dang nges par 'byung //
NK061(ku)001:2226: stobs glang po che'i khri dang /
NK061(ku)001:2228: rgyal ba'i sku la stobs bcu lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2229: rtags glang po che brgyad kyis bteg pa'i khri dang /
NK061(ku)001:2230: de yang don de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu gang zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2232: gnas dang gnas min yang dag mkhyen //
NK061(ku)001:2233: dus gsum las 'bras rnam smin mkhyen //
NK061(ku)001:2234: khams rnams sna tshogs mkhyen pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:2235: pha rol mos pa mkhyen pa'i stobs //
NK061(ku)001:2236: dbang po mchog dang mchog min mkhyen //
NK061(ku)001:2237: kun tu 'gro lam mkhyen pa'i stobs //
NK061(ku)001:2238: bsam gtan thar dang nyon mongs mkhyen //
NK061(ku)001:2239: sngon gyi gnas mkhyen stobs dang ni //
NK061(ku)001:2241: zag pa zag med sems grol mkhyen //
NK061(ku)001:2242: de bcu stobs su gyur pa na //
NK061(ku)001:2243: 'bras bu mngon nas drug yin no //
NK061(ku)001:2247: rgyal ba'i yon tan la rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2248: rtags su rta mchog brgyad kyis bteg pa'i khri dang /
NK061(ku)001:2249: de yang don de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi gang zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2252: spyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin spong ba'i //
NK061(ku)001:2253: 'du byed rnams te rkang pa bzhi //
NK061(ku)001:2254: ye shes bzhi grub 'bras bu ste //
NK061(ku)001:2255: chos dbyings ye shes kun la khyab //
NK061(ku)001:2259: rgyal ba'i gsung la dbang bcu lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2260: rtags su rma bya brgyad kyis bteg pa'i khri dang /
NK061(ku)001:2261: de yang don de bzhin gshegs pa'i dbang bcu gang zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2263: yo byad skye ba tshe la dbang //
NK061(ku)001:2264: ye shes chos dang sems dang las //
NK061(ku)001:2265: rdzu 'phrul smon lam mos rnams kyis //
NK061(ku)001:2266: khams gsum kun gyi dbang phyug rgyal //
NK061(ku)001:2268: thogs pa med pa nam mkha' lding gi khri dang /
NK061(ku)001:2270: rgyal ba'i phrin las la las bzhi lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2271: rtags su thogs pa med pa nam mkha' lding shang
NK061(ku)001:2272: shang gi gzugs can brgyad kyis btegs pa'i khri dang
NK061(ku)001:2273: / de yang don de bzhin gshegs pa'i phrin las bzhi gang zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2275: zhi rgyas dbang drag las rnams kyis //
NK061(ku)001:2276: thogs med las rnams lhun gyis grub //
NK061(ku)001:2277: ci la'ang thogs pa med par spyod //
NK061(ku)001:2279: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las/
NK061(ku)001:2280: thugs ni mi 'jigs bzhi yis bdud bzhi 'joms //
NK061(ku)001:2281: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK061(ku)001:2282: sku ni stobs bcus mi dge bcu rnams 'joms //
NK061(ku)001:2283: de grub rtags su glang chen khri la bzhugs //
NK061(ku)001:2284: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med sgrol //
NK061(ku)001:2285: de grub rtags su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK061(ku)001:2286: gsung ni dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal ba'i gsung //
NK061(ku)001:2287: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK061(ku)001:2288: las ni phrin las bzhi yis thogs med sgrol //
NK061(ku)001:2289: de grub rtags su shang shang khri la bzhugs //
NK061(ku)001:2291: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK061(ku)001:2293: rgyal ba'i thugs rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba ste/
NK061(ku)001:2294: de yang shes rab rang bzhin med pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2295: rtags nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi gdan dang /
NK061(ku)001:2296: thabs snang la 'gag pa med pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2297: rtags zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi gdan dang /
NK061(ku)001:2298: gos pa med pa pad+ma rin po che'i gdan la/
NK061(ku)001:2300: rgyal ba'i thugs la nyes pa'i skyon gyis gos pa med pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2301: rtags sna tshogs pad+ma'i gdan dang /
NK061(ku)001:2302: rgyal ba'i thugs la dgos 'dod lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2303: rtags rin po che'i khri rkang gi gdan la bzhugs pa ste/
NK061(ku)001:2304: de yang dkor bdun ngo bo nyid du lhun gyis grub pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2305: rtags khri rkang re re la yang rin po che'i mdzod mig bdun bdun dang ldan pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2306: de la gdan gyi rim pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2309: sgo ba la nyi ma rkyang pa/
NK061(ku)001:2311: kun bzang yab yum la bzhi brtsegs so //
NK061(ku)001:2312: zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:2314: skyes bu rigs lnga la lnga brtsegs/
NK061(ku)001:2315: sems dpa' yab yum la gsum brtsegs/
NK061(ku)001:2316: sgo ba yab yum la nyi ma dang pad+ma nyis brtsegs/
NK061(ku)001:2317: thub pa la pad+ma rkyang pa/
NK061(ku)001:2318: kun bzang yab yum la dkyil 'khor la 'god pa'i tshe gsum brtsegs dang /
NK061(ku)001:2319: chos 'chad pa'i tshe lnga brtsegs su bshad do //
NK061(ku)001:2320: gdan gyi steng du zla ba 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan ni/
NK061(ku)001:2322: thig le chen po dang sa bon ni thams cad
NK061(ku)001:2323: kyi byed pa po'i phyir bdag po dang rdo rje
NK061(ku)001:2324: ste/ dbus na zla ba ltar gnas so //
NK061(ku)001:2325: zhes pas thabs lam ltar na/
NK061(ku)001:2326: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo na srog mi shigs pa'i thig le dang /
NK061(ku)001:2327: klad pa bde chen gyi 'khor lo na kun tu bzang po'i thig le yod pas/
NK061(ku)001:2328: thabs kyis zin ma zin gyi cha nas thig le
NK061(ku)001:2329: gnyis po de 'khor 'das thams cad kyi byed pa
NK061(ku)001:2332: rgyud kyi bdag po rgyal ba drug pa kun tu bzang po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2333: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' gnyis
NK061(ku)001:2334: la gdan zla ba steng du yod pa'i rgyu mtshan
NK061(ku)001:2335: yin gsung / de yang spyan 'grel las/
NK061(ku)001:2336: gtso bo ni shes rab la spyod pa'i phyir nang
NK061(ku)001:2337: gi chu skyes kyi lte ba la nyi ma brten
NK061(ku)001:2338: pa'i phyir ri bong can steng na gnas so //
NK061(ku)001:2339: yum rnams ni de las ldog go //
NK061(ku)001:2340: zhes 'chad na yang 'khril sbyor gyi phyir gcig par
NK061(ku)001:2341: yang mi 'gal lo zhes gsungs te shes rab kyis
NK061(ku)001:2342: spyod pa'i dbang du/ yum gyi pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa'i lte ba la/
NK061(ku)001:2343: nyi ma byang chub kyi sems yod pa de la/
NK061(ku)001:2344: yab kyi zla ba byang chub kyi sems brten dgos
NK061(ku)001:2345: pa'i phyir zla ba steng du 'ong ba yin gsung
NK061(ku)001:2346: ngo // rje drings pa nye'u ston chos kyi seng ge na re/
NK061(ku)001:2347: gtso bos thabs snang la 'gag pa med pas zla ba steng du 'ong ba yin gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:2348: yang zhi ba la lha kun la zla ba steng du 'ong la/
NK061(ku)001:2349: khro bo la lha kun la nyi ma steng du
NK061(ku)001:2350: yong bar yang 'grel pa mngon rtogs ltar rung ngo
NK061(ku)001:2351: // yang 'ga' zhig sems can gyi gdan 'di dag
NK061(ku)001:2352: /rang snang sprul pa ba yin nam rang rgyud pa
NK061(ku)001:2353: yin zhes pa'i brgal lan las/
NK061(ku)001:2355: lan ni dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las/
NK061(ku)001:2356: thugs ni mi 'jigs bzhi yis bdud bzhi 'joms //
NK061(ku)001:2357: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK061(ku)001:2360: ye shes chen po mngon du byas pa'i rig pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2361: 'bras bu'i chos bzhi dang bcu gnyis dang /
NK061(ku)001:2362: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid yongs su rdzogs pas/
NK061(ku)001:2367: spar khab kyi lung gong du bshad pa dang 'gal lo zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2369: spyir gnyis ka ltar du rung yang /
NK061(ku)001:2370: gzhung 'dir bkod pa rnams thugs rang snang du 'thad de/
NK061(ku)001:2371: gong gi mngon rtogs kyi lung gis gsal bas/
NK061(ku)001:2372: 'di dag thugs rang snang gtso che'o //
NK061(ku)001:2373: de dang cha mthun pa'i rgyud mas sbyangs kyang yod ces bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:2374: de ltar sa dmigs lnga po des gang du gsungs
NK061(ku)001:2375: pa'i gnas phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bstan pa
NK061(ku)001:2377: dga' bde yang dag rdzogs pa'i gnas //
NK061(ku)001:2378: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK061(ku)001:2379: ma lus 'dus pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK061(ku)001:2380: bdag po rgyan dang bcas pa nyid //
NK061(ku)001:2382: nyis 'gyur shin tu spags pa na //
NK061(ku)001:2383: ngo bo mtha' gsum las 'das pa //
NK061(ku)001:2384: ma spangs rgyan tshogs gzhal yas khang //
NK061(ku)001:2385: yon tan lnga yi bdag po ste //
NK061(ku)001:2386: gru bzhi spyi bor 'khyil snang ba'o //
NK061(ku)001:2388: spyi don gsum pa gang la gsungs pa'i 'khor phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bstan pa la gnyis te/
NK061(ku)001:2389: rang bzhin nam dgongs pa gnyis su med pa'i 'khor dang /
NK061(ku)001:2390: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor ro //
NK061(ku)001:2391: dang po rang bzhin nam dgongs pa gnyis su med pa'i 'khor la gnyis te/
NK061(ku)001:2392: rigs kyi yab lnga sku mdog dang bcas pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2393: rigs kyi yum lnga gnyis su med par bzhugs tshul tshad dang bcas pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2394: dang po rigs kyi yab lnga sku mdog dang bcas pa bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2395: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang ljang gu'i mdog tu 'tsher ba/
NK061(ku)001:2397: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa zhes pa mtshan thun mong ba gnyis ni/
NK061(ku)001:2398: sngar bshad pa'i ston pa'i rang bzhin dang 'bru mthun la/
NK061(ku)001:2399: rnam par shes pa'i zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2400: rnam par shes pa spyi'i mtshan nyid yul rig pa yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2401: bye brag tu phye na tshogs brgyad do //
NK061(ku)001:2406: de ltar brgyad kyi tshogs pa ni rnam par shes pa'i phung po'o //
NK061(ku)001:2408: de lta bu'i rtog pa tshogs brgyad kyi phung po'i rang bzhin/
NK061(ku)001:2409: ye ji bzhin pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' yin pa las/
NK061(ku)001:2410: khyad par rgyud dag pa'i rdo rje sems dpa'i 'bras bu mngon du byas te/
NK061(ku)001:2411: mthar phyin par gyur pa'am rtog pa de lta bu la/
NK061(ku)001:2412: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis rang dbang sgyur cing /
NK061(ku)001:2413: zag pa med pa'i chos la mnga' brnyes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2414: bde ba chen por longs spyod pa'i phyir na rgyal po zhes bya'o //
NK061(ku)001:2415: de ltar rtogs pa rnam par shes pa'i phung po
NK061(ku)001:2416: nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa lha ni bcom
NK061(ku)001:2417: ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa'/
NK061(ku)001:2418: don du ni rnam par grol ba'i ye shes gzigs pa'i phung po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2419: de bzhin gshegs pa gzugs kyi rgyal po dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2420: de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'bru mthun/
NK061(ku)001:2421: gzugs kyi rgyal po dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2422: gzugs spyi'i mtshan nyid gzhig cing gzhom du rung ba yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2425: rgyu'i gzugs sa chu me rlung bzhi dang /
NK061(ku)001:2426: 'bras bu'i gzugs mig rna ba sna lce lus kyi dbang po lnga dang /
NK061(ku)001:2427: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya ste don du snang ba yum lnga dang /
NK061(ku)001:2428: rnam par rig byed ma yin pa'i gzugs te so sor thar pa'i sdom pa la sogs pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2429: de ltar gzugs chos bco lnga po rnams kyi rtog pa la rang dbang sgyur bas na rgyal po ste/
NK061(ku)001:2430: rtog pa gzugs kyi phung po nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2431: lha ni rnam par snang mdzad/
NK061(ku)001:2432: don du ni rnam par grol ba'i phung po/
NK061(ku)001:2433: de bzhin gshegs pa tshor ba'i rgyal po dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2434: de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'bru mthun/
NK061(ku)001:2435: tshor ba spyi'i mtshan nyid nyams su myong ba dang bcas pa yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2436: bye brag tu phye na tshor ba gsal dang mi gsal bar ma gsum mam/
NK061(ku)001:2437: bde sdug btang snyoms gsum gyi tshor ba'i rtog pa la rang dbang sgyur bas na rgyal po ste/
NK061(ku)001:2438: rtog pa tshor ba'i phung po nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2440: don du ni tshul khrims kyi phung po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2441: de bzhin gshegs pa 'du shes kyi rgyal po dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2442: de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'bru mthun/
NK061(ku)001:2443: 'du shes spyi'i mtshan nyid yul la mtshan mar 'dzin pa yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2445: rgya che ba chung ba tshad med pa gsum gyi
NK061(ku)001:2446: 'du shes kyi rtog pa la rang dbang sgyur bas
NK061(ku)001:2447: na rgyal po ste/ rtog pa 'du shes kyi phung po nyid ma spangs rang gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2448: lha ni snang ba mtha' yas/
NK061(ku)001:2449: don du ni ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2450: de bzhin gshegs pa 'du byed kyi rgyal po dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2451: de bzhin gshegs pa ni 'bru mthun/
NK061(ku)001:2452: 'du byed spyi'i mtshan nyid mngon par 'du byed pa yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2458: sems dpa' ste kun tu 'gro ba lnga dang/
NK061(ku)001:2463: shes rab ste yul so sor nges pa lnga dang /
NK061(ku)001:2467: ma chags pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba dang /
NK061(ku)001:2468: zhe sdang med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba dang /
NK061(ku)001:2469: gti mug med pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba dang /
NK061(ku)001:2474: rnam par mi 'tshe ba ste dge ba bcu gcig dang /
NK061(ku)001:2480: the tshom ste rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa drug dang /
NK061(ku)001:2500: shes bzhin ma yin pa ste nye ba'i nyon mongs pa nyi shu dang /
NK061(ku)001:2504: spyod pa ste gzhan du 'gyur ba bzhi/
NK061(ku)001:2505: de ltar sems las byung ba'i chos lnga bcu rtsa gcig ste/
NK061(ku)001:2506: 'du byed kyi rtog pa la rang dbang sgyur ba'i phyir rgyal po'o //
NK061(ku)001:2507: de ltar rtog pa 'du byed kyi phung po nyid ma spangs pa gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2508: lha ni bcom ldan 'das dpal don yod grub pa/
NK061(ku)001:2509: don du ni shes rab kyi phung po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2510: de dag kun kyang 'tsher ba zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2511: rigs lnga po de dag kun kyang rang bzhin gyi
NK061(ku)001:2512: sku mdog bzhi ni dung ltar nyes pa'i skyon gyis
NK061(ku)001:2513: ma gos pa/ me tog ku mu ta'i mdog ltar snum la 'dril ba/
NK061(ku)001:2516: rigs kyi sku mdog lnga ni/
NK061(ku)001:2517: chos nyid mi 'gyur bar mtshon pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2518: rtags rdo rje'i rigs kun sku mdog mthing kha dang /
NK061(ku)001:2519: nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2520: rtags de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kun sku mdog dkar po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2521: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2522: rtags rin po che'i rigs kun sku mdog ser po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2523: gdul bya'i don la chags pa mtshon pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2524: rtags pad+ma'i rigs kun sku mdog le brgan te dmar po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2525: las sna tshogs lhun gyis grub par mdzad pa don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2526: rtags las kyi rigs kun sku mdog ljang khu'i mdog can te/
NK061(ku)001:2527: sku mdog de dag kyang ma 'dres par/
NK061(ku)001:2528: rang rang gi kha dog tu 'tsher ba'o //
NK061(ku)001:2529: 'o na skabs 'dir rdo rje sems dpa' dang bya ba la sogs par mi 'ong bar/
NK061(ku)001:2530: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang zhes pa la
NK061(ku)001:2531: sogs pa rtog pa smos pa la dgos pa ci
NK061(ku)001:2532: yod ce na/ spar khab las/
NK061(ku)001:2533: kun gzhi la sogs pa'i rtog pa lnga smos pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2534: rang bzhin dang thun mong ma yin pa'i phyir smos pa ste/
NK061(ku)001:2535: de dag kar dag par chud pa la rdo rje
NK061(ku)001:2536: 'dzin pa la sogs par rang snang ba'i phyir ro
NK061(ku)001:2538: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba'i dbang du/
NK061(ku)001:2539: rang bzhin gyi phyir smos pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2540: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba'i dbang du/
NK061(ku)001:2541: thun mong ma yin pa'i phyir smos pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2542: 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba'i dbang du/
NK061(ku)001:2543: kar dag par thugs su chud pa'i phyir snang ba'o //
NK061(ku)001:2544: dang po ni rang bzhin shes bya'i gshis la/
NK061(ku)001:2545: rtog pa rnam par shes pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2546: 'bras bu rdo rje sems dpa' gnyis snang na snang mnyam stong na stong mnyam/
NK061(ku)001:2547: bzang ngan med pas kyang smos pa yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2548: gnyis pa ni thun mong gi theg pa'i skabs su lha smos pa/
NK061(ku)001:2549: thun mong ma yin pa'i rgyud 'di'i skabs su rtog pa smos pas/
NK061(ku)001:2550: lha dang rtog pa dbyer med du ngos zin par bya ba'i phyir smos pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2551: gsum pa ni lam nyams su blangs pas 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dus tsam na/
NK061(ku)001:2552: rnam par shes pa nyid ma spangs ma bsgyur bar
NK061(ku)001:2553: rdo rje sems dpar rang snang ba'i phyir du'ang smos
NK061(ku)001:2554: pa'o // de'i phyir rtog pa smos pa thams cad de ltar shes par bya'o //
NK061(ku)001:2555: gnyis pa rigs kyi yum lnga gnyis su med par bzhugs tshul tshad dang bcas par bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2556: btsun mo dam pa snang ba'i dbyings dang khyab par bzhugs so //
NK061(ku)001:2558: btsun mo zhes pas rtog pa'i skabs su skyed par byed pa'i rgyur gyur pas na btsun mo ste/
NK061(ku)001:2559: 'byung ba lngas phung po lnga bskyed pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2560: de yang 'grel pa mngon rtogs las/
NK061(ku)001:2561: sems can gyi dus na phung po bskyed pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2562: brten pa'i gzhi 'byung bas te zhes pas gsal lo //
NK061(ku)001:2563: lha'i skabs su skyed par bya ba'i yul du gyur bas kyang btsun mo ste/
NK061(ku)001:2564: shes rab yum la thabs yab kyis rol pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2565: dam pa zhes pas rang bzhin dang /
NK061(ku)001:2566: sems ma las khyad par du gyur pas dam pa/
NK061(ku)001:2567: snang ba zhes pa nam mkha'i mtshan nyid yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2568: sras kyi tshogs kyi 'byung khungs sam bde ba'i ye shes bskyed pa'i rgyur gyur pa'i phyir na dbyings te/
NK061(ku)001:2569: 'byung ba nam mkhar 'dzin pa'i rtog pa nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2570: lha ni yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma dang btsun
NK061(ku)001:2571: mo dam pa 'di na mar la med kyang 'jug
NK061(ku)001:2573: sra ba'i dbyings dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2574: sra ba'i zhes pa sa'i mtshan nyid yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2576: 'byung ba sar 'dzin pa'i rtog pa nyid ma spangs dbyings su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2577: lha ni yum sangs rgyas spyan ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2578: mnyen pa'i dbyings dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2579: mnyen pa chu'i mtshan nyid yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2580: 'byung ba chur 'dzin pa'i rtog pa nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2581: lha ni yum chen mo dbyings phyug ma m+aa ma k+ai dang /
NK061(ku)001:2582: dro ba'i dbyings dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2583: dro ba me'i mtshan nyid yid la/
NK061(ku)001:2584: 'byung ba mer 'dzin pa'i rtog pa nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2585: lha ni yum chen mo dbyings phyug ma gos dkar mo dang /
NK061(ku)001:2587: bskyod pa rlung gi mtshan nyid yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2588: 'byung ba rlung du 'dzin pa'i rtog pa nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2589: lha ni yum chen mo dbyings phyug ma dam tshig sgrol ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2590: la sogs pa'i sogs khongs nas de dag dang cha
NK061(ku)001:2591: lugs mthun pa'i rgyud mas sbyangs kyi rigs lnga yab
NK061(ku)001:2593: btsun mo'i tshogs dang khyab par bzhugs so zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2594: de yang shes rab kyi rgyud ltar na/
NK061(ku)001:2595: btsun mo'i tshogs kyi dbus na/
NK061(ku)001:2596: rigs lnga yab dang yum gnyis su med par bzhugs shing /
NK061(ku)001:2597: chos kyi dbyings kun tu mtha' yas par khyab pa'i rang bzhin mngon du byas pa'am/
NK061(ku)001:2598: bdag nyid chen po ni don yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2599: rtags su khang pa lhas gang ba 'di lta ste/
NK061(ku)001:2600: dper na til gyi gang bu la til 'bras kyis khyab la/
NK061(ku)001:2601: til 'bras la til mar gyis khyab pa bzhin du
NK061(ku)001:2602: gzhal yas khang lhas gang nas kun tu khyab par
NK061(ku)001:2603: bzhugs so // gnyis pa rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor la gsum ste/
NK061(ku)001:2606: 'khor de dag mang ba dang khyab pa'i tshad dang gnyis su med par bzhugs pa'i tshul bstan pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2607: dang po rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor la gnyis te/
NK061(ku)001:2608: nang sems yab yum brgyad bstan pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2609: phyi sems yab yum brgyad bstan pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2610: dang po nang sems yab yum brgyad bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2611: de nas byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong ba myong bar bya ba'i tshogs dang /
NK061(ku)001:2614: 'brel mtshams sbyor ba'i tshig bya ngang mo'i 'gros ltar du bshad na/
NK061(ku)001:2615: rang bzhin nam dgongs pa gnyis med kyi 'khor bstan
NK061(ku)001:2616: pa la de rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor
NK061(ku)001:2617: ston pas na nas/ byang chub chen po rdo rje
NK061(ku)001:2618: zhes pas rgyud mas sbyangs ltar du 'bru bsnan na
NK061(ku)001:2619: shes rab chen pos chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu
NK061(ku)001:2621: snying rje chen pos sems can gyi don la sems pas na chub/
NK061(ku)001:2622: ces bla ma gong ma rnams gsung la/
NK061(ku)001:2623: bstan pa'i mnga' bdag 'jam dbyangs chen po bsam grub rdo rje'i gsung gis/
NK061(ku)001:2624: shes rab chen pos bdag don du sgrib pa byang zhing /
NK061(ku)001:2625: rang sa'i yon tan rdzogs pa'i phyir chub/
NK061(ku)001:2626: sems dpa' zhor la bshad na/
NK061(ku)001:2627: snying rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don las sems pa'i phyir sems/
NK061(ku)001:2628: bdag gzhan gyi sgrib pa 'joms pa la dpa' ba'i phyir dpa' zhes byas na 'thad gsung /
NK061(ku)001:2629: mtshan nyid byang chub sems dpa' la khyad par du gyur pas chen po/
NK061(ku)001:2630: lta ba'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir rdo rje'o //
NK061(ku)001:2631: thugs rig pa rang snang ltar du 'bru bsnan na/
NK061(ku)001:2632: rtog pa mig gi rnam par shes pa bdag tu 'dzin pa byang /
NK061(ku)001:2633: 'bras bu lha'i snying po'i skur gsal bas chub/
NK061(ku)001:2634: rgyud mas sbyangs kyi byang chub sems dpa' las khyad par du gyur pas chen po/
NK061(ku)001:2635: lta ba sgrib pa chom zin pas rdo rje/
NK061(ku)001:2637: mthong ba mig gi rnam par shes pa nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2638: lha ni byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2639: byang chub chen po rdo rje thos pa dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2640: byang chub chen po rdo rje 'bru mthun la/
NK061(ku)001:2641: thos pa rna ba'i rnam par shes pa nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2642: lha ni byang chub sems dpa' phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK061(ku)001:2643: byang chub chen po rdo rje snom pa dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2644: snom pa sna'i rnam par shes pa nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2645: lha ni byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2646: byang chub chen po rdo rje myong ba dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2647: myong ba lce'i rnam par shes pa nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2648: lha ni byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
NK061(ku)001:2649: btsun mo zhes pa ni sngar bshad pa dang 'bru mthun la/
NK061(ku)001:2650: skabs 'dir yul bzhis rnam shes bzhi bskyed pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2651: mthong bar bya ba dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2652: mthong bar bya ba gzugs kyi skye mched ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2653: lha ni lha mo l+aa s+ye ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2654: mnyan par bya ba dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2655: mnyan par bya ba sgra'i skye mched ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2656: lha ni lha mo n+airti ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2659: mnam par bya ba dri'i skye mched ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2660: lha ni lha mo m+aa le ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2661: myong bar bya ba'i zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2662: myong bar bya ba ro'i skye mched ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2663: lha ni lha mo girti ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2665: de dang cha lugs mthun pa'i rgyud mas sbyangs kyi nang sems yab yum kyang bsdu'o //
NK061(ku)001:2666: gnyis pa phyi sems yab yum brgyad bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2667: byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong byed ma byon pa'i tshogs dang /
NK061(ku)001:2669: byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong byed dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2670: byang chub chen po rdo rje ni 'bru mthun la/
NK061(ku)001:2671: mthong byed mig gi dbang po ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2672: lha ni byang chub sems dpa' byams pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2673: byang chub chen po rdo rje thos byed dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2674: thos byed rna ba'i dbang po ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2675: lha ni byang chub sems dpa' sgrib pa sel ba dang /
NK061(ku)001:2676: byang chub chen po rdo rje snom byed dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2677: snom byed sna'i dbang po ma spangs gnas su dag pal/
NK061(ku)001:2678: lha ni byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2679: byang chub chen po myong byed dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2680: myong byed lce'i dbang po ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2681: lha ni byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal gzhon nu dang /
NK061(ku)001:2682: btsun mo 'das pa dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2683: btsun mo ni sngar bzhin la/
NK061(ku)001:2684: khyad par du skabs 'dir dus bzhis dbang po bzhi bskyed pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2686: 'das pa'i dus ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2687: lha ni lha mo d+hu pe ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2689: da ltar ba'i dus ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2690: lha ni lha mo push+pe ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2692: phyis 'byung ba'i dus ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2693: lha ni lha mo +aa lo ke dang /
NK061(ku)001:2694: ma byon pa'i dus so zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2695: ma byon pa ste 'byung bar ma nges pa'i dus ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2696: lha ni lha mo gan+d+he ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2698: de dag dang cha lugs mthun pa'i rgyud mas sbyangs
NK061(ku)001:2699: kyi phyi sems yab yum rnams kyi tshogs dang bcas
NK061(ku)001:2700: pa'o // gsum pa 'joms byed khro bo'i 'khor bstan pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2701: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg pa mtshan mar 'dzin pa la sogs pa/
NK061(ku)001:2704: khro bo rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pas
NK061(ku)001:2705: bdud dang mu stegs la sogs pa'i dpung 'joms pas
NK061(ku)001:2706: na 'joms pa/ chen po ni bdag la sgrib pa mi gsog gzhan la sdug bsngal mi bskyed pa'i phyir/
NK061(ku)001:2707: bdud dang gnod sbyin la sogs pa las khyad par du gyur pas chen po/
NK061(ku)001:2709: lta ba'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir las kyi rdo rje'o //
NK061(ku)001:2710: reg pa dang zhes pa ni gsang ba'i bdag po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2711: yul dang rnam par shes pa ste gsum 'dus kyi
NK061(ku)001:2712: reg pa'am lus ngag yid gsum spyir 'dzin pa nyid
NK061(ku)001:2713: ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2714: lha ni khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK061(ku)001:2715: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg byed dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2716: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje ni 'bru mthun la/
NK061(ku)001:2717: reg byed ni gsang ba'i bdag po thabs kyi rdo
NK061(ku)001:2718: rje'am bdag tu 'dzin pa nyid ma spangs gnas su
NK061(ku)001:2719: dag pa/ lha ni khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK061(ku)001:2720: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg bya ni/
NK061(ku)001:2721: gsang ba'i yul shes rab kyi pad+ma'am lus su 'dzin pa nyid ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2722: lha ni khro bo chen po stobs po che dang /
NK061(ku)001:2723: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje 'bru mthun la/
NK061(ku)001:2724: reg shes ni gsang ba'i rnam par shes pas dga'
NK061(ku)001:2725: ba nyams su myong ba'am yid du 'dzin pa nyid
NK061(ku)001:2726: ma spangs gnas su dag pa/
NK061(ku)001:2727: lha ni khro bo chen po gshin rje'i gshed po dang /
NK061(ku)001:2728: btsun mo rtag par ma yin pa dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2729: btsun mo ni sngar bshad pa bzhin las/
NK061(ku)001:2731: rtag chad kyi phyi log bzhis lus kyi rtog gzhi
NK061(ku)001:2732: dngos su mi skyed kyang brgyud nas skyes gsung ngo
NK061(ku)001:2733: // rtag par ma yin pa dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2734: nga'am rdzas kyi dngos po la rtag par 'dzin pa
NK061(ku)001:2735: nyid rang kha mar ma yin pa ste de ma
NK061(ku)001:2737: lha ni khro mo lcags kyu ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2738: chad par ma yin pa dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2739: nga'am rdzas kyi dngos po la chad par 'dzin pa
NK061(ku)001:2740: nyid rang kha mar ma yin te de ma spangs
NK061(ku)001:2741: gnas su dag pa/ lha ni khro mo zhags pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2742: bdag tu ma yin pa dang zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2743: nga'am rdzas kyi dngos po la bdag tu 'dzin pa
NK061(ku)001:2744: nyid rang kha mar ma yin pa ste de ma
NK061(ku)001:2746: lha ni khro mo lcags sgrog ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2747: mtshan mar ma yin pa zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:2748: nga'am rdzas kyi dngos po la mtshan mar 'dzin pa
NK061(ku)001:2749: nyid rang kha mar ma yin pa ste de ma
NK061(ku)001:2751: lha ni khro mo dril bu ma dang /
NK061(ku)001:2752: la sogs pa zhes pa'i sogs khongs nas de dag
NK061(ku)001:2753: dang cha lugs mthun pa'i rgyud mas sbyangs kyi khro
NK061(ku)001:2754: bo yab yum rnams kyang sdud do //
NK061(ku)001:2755: gsum pa 'khor de dag mang ba dang khyab pa'i
NK061(ku)001:2756: tshad gnyis su med par bzhugs pa'i tshul bstan pa
NK061(ku)001:2757: ni/ de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK061(ku)001:2759: rgyud mas sbyangs kyi dbang du/
NK061(ku)001:2760: gong du bshad pa de lta bu'i 'khor gyi tshogs grangs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang /
NK061(ku)001:2761: rigs kyi yab lnga dang rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa gnyis su med par bzhugs/
NK061(ku)001:2762: rigs kyi yum lnga dang thabs shes rab gnyis su med par bzhugs/
NK061(ku)001:2763: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor dang bcas gnyis su med par bzhugs/
NK061(ku)001:2764: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi'i dbang du lha dang rtogs pa gnyis su med par bzhugs/
NK061(ku)001:2765: dad pa gtam nyan gyi 'khor dang rang bzhin gnyis su med par bzhugs/
NK061(ku)001:2766: thugs rig pa rang snang gi dbang du gong du
NK061(ku)001:2767: bshad pa de lta bu'i tshogs grangs brjod kyis mi
NK061(ku)001:2768: lang ba dang / ston 'khor gnyis bzang ngan dang
NK061(ku)001:2769: che chung tha dad med pa'i phyir gnyis su med
NK061(ku)001:2770: lang ba dang / par bzhugs so // de ltar
NK061(ku)001:2771: bshad pa'i le'u dang po'i 'khor 'di dag /thugs rig
NK061(ku)001:2772: pa rang snang sprul pa ba 'ba' zhig yin nam/
NK061(ku)001:2773: rgyud mas sbyangs rang rgyud pa zhig yin/
NK061(ku)001:2774: dang po ltar na le'u dang po'i 'khor rnams chos can/
NK061(ku)001:2775: mas sbyangs gtan nas med par thal/
NK061(ku)001:2776: thugs rig pa rang snang 'ba' zhig tu 'dod kyi 'dug pa'i phyir/
NK061(ku)001:2779: dang po bka' lung dang 'gal ba'i skyon ni/
NK061(ku)001:2781: dang po'i sangs rgyas sa rgyal ba //
NK061(ku)001:2782: sems dpa' che dang 'joms pa che //
NK061(ku)001:2783: brjod kyis mi lang tshad med dang //
NK061(ku)001:2786: de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK061(ku)001:2788: gnyis pa man ngag dang 'gal ba'i skyon ni/
NK061(ku)001:2790: gdul bya las mthar thug pa ni drug pa'i zhing du 'gyur te/
NK061(ku)001:2791: de dag pa gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas chen po/
NK061(ku)001:2792: lta ba'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir las kyi rdo rje'o //
NK061(ku)001:2794: mas sbyangs mthar phyin pa'i lam gyi byang sems shes sgrib can du bshad pas gsal zhing /
NK061(ku)001:2795: gsum pa rig pa dang 'gal ba'i skyon ni/
NK061(ku)001:2796: rang snang sprul pa ba chos can/
NK061(ku)001:2798: rang snang sprul pa pa'i lugs kyis mas sbyangs rang
NK061(ku)001:2799: rgyud pa 'dul ba la dgongs pa yin pa la
NK061(ku)001:2800: mas sbyangs rang rgyud pa gtan nas med pa'i phyir/
NK061(ku)001:2802: sprul pa ba yin pa'i dam bca' 'bud/
NK061(ku)001:2803: 'dod na gong gi lung man ngag gis gsal lo //
NK061(ku)001:2806: rang snang sprul pa ba gtan nas med par thal/
NK061(ku)001:2807: rang rgyud pa 'ba' zhig yin pa'i phyir/
NK061(ku)001:2810: dang po bka' lung dang 'gal ba'i skyon ni/
NK061(ku)001:2812: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK061(ku)001:2813: rang snang rgyal ba'i sems sogs dang //
NK061(ku)001:2814: zhes pas rgyal ba'i thugs rig pa rang snang du bshad la/
NK061(ku)001:2815: gnyis pa man ngag dang 'gal ba'i skyon ni/
NK061(ku)001:2817: mtshan thun mong ba gnyis ni sngar thal te zhes dang /
NK061(ku)001:2818: rang rig pa nyid gsum gyi khyad par du snang ba la ngam pa gsum mo zhes dang /
NK061(ku)001:2819: kar dag pa thugs su chud pa las rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs par rang snang ba'i phyir/
NK061(ku)001:2821: yang rtog tshogs ma smos pa rjes su thun mong /
NK061(ku)001:2823: ston 'khor gnas gsum rgyal ba drug pa'i thugs rig pa rang snang du gsungs pas gsal zhing /
NK061(ku)001:2824: gsum pa rig pa dang 'gal ba'i skyon ni/
NK061(ku)001:2825: le'u dang por smos pa'i rtog pa 'di rnams gang zag tha dad kyi rtog pa yin nam/
NK061(ku)001:2826: gang zag gcig gi rtog pa yin/
NK061(ku)001:2828: gang zag gcig la yang rtog pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ma tshang bar thal/
NK061(ku)001:2829: tha dad kyi rtog pa yin pa'i phyir/
NK061(ku)001:2832: 'dod na gcig gi rtog pa las ma smos pas gsal/
NK061(ku)001:2833: yang gang zag gcig gi rtog pa yin zer na/
NK061(ku)001:2834: yid chos phung po dang 'byung ba lnga sangs rgyas nas 'dug la/
NK061(ku)001:2835: rnam shes dang dbang po ni byang chub pa'i rgyud du 'dug pas/
NK061(ku)001:2837: gang zag gcig gi rgyud la sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i rgyud gnyis 'dug pa'i phyir/
NK061(ku)001:2838: gtan tshigs ma grub na gcig gi dam bca' 'bud/
NK061(ku)001:2844: rje dri ngas pa nye'u ston chos kyi seng ge'i bzhed kyis/
NK061(ku)001:2845: le'u dang po dngos su byung ba rtog tshogs dang
NK061(ku)001:2846: sbyar ba'i 'khor 'di rnams thugs rig pa rang snang
NK061(ku)001:2848: rgyud mas sbyangs rang rgyud pa gtan nas med pa ma yin te/
NK061(ku)001:2849: tshogs bya ba'i khongs nas de rnams dang cha lugs mthun pa'i sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK061(ku)001:2850: theg pa 'og ma pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa la gnas pa'ang yod gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:2851: de bka' lung gnyis ka dang mi 'gal te/
NK061(ku)001:2852: rang rgyud pa gtan nas med par khas ma blangs te yod pas so //
NK061(ku)001:2854: mas sbyangs yod pas sprul pa ba ni de 'dul ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2855: de bsgrub pa la gsum las/
NK061(ku)001:2856: dang po bka' lung gis bsgrub pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2858: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK061(ku)001:2859: rang snang rgyal ba'i sems sogs dang //
NK061(ku)001:2860: dang po'i sangs rgyas sa rgyal ba //
NK061(ku)001:2861: sems dpa' che dang 'joms pa che //
NK061(ku)001:2862: brjod kyis mi lang tshad med dang //
NK061(ku)001:2863: rnam gnyis tshul du bzhugs pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2864: zhes sprul pa ba dang rang rgyud pa gnyis kar bshad pa'i phyir dang /
NK061(ku)001:2865: gnyis pa man ngag gis bsgrub pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2867: gdul bya las mthar thug pa ni drug pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du 'gyur te/
NK061(ku)001:2869: rgyud mas sbyangs ltar bshad pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2870: rang rig pa nyid gsum gyi khyad par du snang ba la ngam pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2872: sprul pa bltar bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK061(ku)001:2873: gsum pa rig pas bsgrub pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2874: dngos su bkod pa 'di 'dul byed sprul pa ba yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2875: de dang cha mthun gyi gdul bya mas sbyangs rang
NK061(ku)001:2876: rgyud pa'ang yod pas sprul pa ba la dgos pa
NK061(ku)001:2878: 'dir gnyis ka ltar bshad nas 'dug pas grub bo gsung /
NK061(ku)001:2879: gtsang pa byi ston gyi bzhed kyis/
NK061(ku)001:2880: sprul pa ba dang rang rgyud pa gnyis ka ltar yin gsungs te/
NK061(ku)001:2881: bka' lung gis bsgrub pa gong dang mthun la/
NK061(ku)001:2882: man ngag gis bsgrub pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2884: gsang ba'i tan+t+ra ston pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:2885: de bzhin bsdu ba mdzad pa dang //
NK061(ku)001:2886: dman lus bsod nams ldan gnas su //
NK061(ku)001:2887: sna tshogs lus can rigs la bkod //
NK061(ku)001:2890: sdud pa po yang mdzad pas sprul pa ba yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2891: bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa cha phra mo yod pas rang rgyud pa yin yang /
NK061(ku)001:2892: mthar lam gyi byang chub sems dpa' bzhed do gsung /
NK061(ku)001:2893: gtsang pa 'od 'bar rje dri ngas pa ltar 'thad gsung /
NK061(ku)001:2894: bla ma rgya gab gong pa'i bzhed kyis rigs lnga yan chad sprul pa ba yin la/
NK061(ku)001:2895: sems dpa' man chad rang rgyud du 'thad do //
NK061(ku)001:2896: de yang mas sbyangs kyi rigs lnga gtan med dang /
NK061(ku)001:2897: yas sprul gyi sems dpa' gtan med du 'dod pa
NK061(ku)001:2898: yin gyis rgya mtsho 'di nyid spar khab gsum dpang
NK061(ku)001:2899: por bzhag pa'i lung gis gsal la/
NK061(ku)001:2900: spyir sprul pa rang rgyud gnyis bsgrub byed la/
NK061(ku)001:2901: bka' lung man ngag gnyis 'thad cing /
NK061(ku)001:2902: rig pas bsgrub pa de dag don chung gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:2904: le'u dang po gleng gzhi'i le'u 'dir/
NK061(ku)001:2905: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis tshang ngam ma tshang /
NK061(ku)001:2908: thub pa drug mi 'dug pas gsal/
NK061(ku)001:2909: ma tshang na gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs par mi 'gyur la/
NK061(ku)001:2910: le'u gnyis par kun tu bzang mo byung /
NK061(ku)001:2911: gsum par thub pa drug byung bas rgyu med kyi 'bras bu 'byung bas skyon yang 'ong ngo zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2912: de lta bu'i skyon mi 'ong ba'i zin so yod de/
NK061(ku)001:2913: thabs dang shes rab ces pas/
NK061(ku)001:2914: shes rab la yum kun tu bzang mo ngos 'dzin/
NK061(ku)001:2915: sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba zhes pas thub pa drug ngos 'dzin no //
NK061(ku)001:2916: des na gleng gzhi ma 'tshogs pa'i skyon med cing
NK061(ku)001:2917: rgyu med kyi 'bras bu 'byung ba'i skyon yang med
NK061(ku)001:2918: do // gsal bar ma byung ba'i 'thad pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2919: le'u dang po gsang dbang gi skabs min pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2920: thun mong gi gdul bya med pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2922: le'u dang po kun tu bzang mo dang thub pa drug gsal bar ma byung la/
NK061(ku)001:2923: le'u gnyis par dbang bskur ba'i don du kun tu bzang mo byung ba yin/
NK061(ku)001:2924: le'u gsum pa dang drug par dkyil 'khor du 'khod pa'i 'khor dang /
NK061(ku)001:2925: 'gro ba 'dul byed kyi 'khor yin pas thub pa drug 'byung ba yin no zhes gsung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:2926: yang 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang na/
NK061(ku)001:2927: sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bzhugs sam mi bzhugs/
NK061(ku)001:2928: bzhugs na thub pa drug gi gdul bya'i zhing rigs drug yin pas/
NK061(ku)001:2929: rigs drug gi sems can 'og min na yod pa'i skyon 'ong la/
NK061(ku)001:2930: mi bzhugs na gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa ma yin pa'i skyon 'ong ngo zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2931: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems can 'og min na yod kyang /
NK061(ku)001:2932: nges pa'i shes pa ma skyes pa yin/
NK061(ku)001:2933: de yang sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las/
NK061(ku)001:2934: yang dag shes pa'i rang rig blo med na //
NK061(ku)001:2935: bde gshegs zhing yang ngan song gnas su mthong //
NK061(ku)001:2936: theg mchog mnyam pa'i don nyid rtogs pas na //
NK061(ku)001:2937: ngan song gnas kyang 'og min dga' ldan gnas //
NK061(ku)001:2939: spyi don gsum pa gleng gzhi bsdus te bstan pa la gsum ste/
NK061(ku)001:2940: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2941: gleng gzhi bsdus pa nges tshig dang bcas pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2942: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig go //
NK061(ku)001:2943: dang po gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2944: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK061(ku)001:2946: de nas zhes pa 'brel mtshams sbyor ba'i tshig ste/
NK061(ku)001:2947: gzhung rgyas par bstan pa la de bsdus te ston pas na nas/
NK061(ku)001:2948: de bzhin gshegs pa yab rgyal ba drug pa nyid/
NK061(ku)001:2949: yum btsun mo'i tshogs dang thabs shes rab gnyis su
NK061(ku)001:2950: med par 'byor ba'i bde ba chen po la 'bras
NK061(ku)001:2951: bu ril lhun gyis grub pa de rtogs dka' ba'i
NK061(ku)001:2953: de dag nyid kyi don nyams su myong dka' bas
NK061(ku)001:2954: gsang ba 'di nyid rigs thams cad kyi bdag nyid
NK061(ku)001:2955: ston pa drug pa kun tu bzang po'i sku dang
NK061(ku)001:2956: gsung dang thugs dang yon tan dang phrin las lnga'i
NK061(ku)001:2957: ngo bo 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga'o //
NK061(ku)001:2958: de dag kyang gcig dang du ma'i mtha' dang bral ba'i phyir/
NK061(ku)001:2959: de lnga dbyer mi byed pas rdo rje ste/
NK061(ku)001:2960: rgyal ba kun tu bzang po'i thugs rig pa de nyid las/
NK061(ku)001:2961: bsdu ba'i don 'di dag mngon sum du snang bas na phyung ngo zhes tha snyad btags pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2962: gnyis pa gleng gzhi bsdus pa nges tshig dang bcas pa ni/
NK061(ku)001:2963: e e ma e ma hoh de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid rdo rje mchog gi gnas nyid do //
NK061(ku)001:2966: gzhung rgyas pa dang sbyar te bsdu ba kho na las ma gsungs kyang /
NK061(ku)001:2967: bla ma brgyud pa'i gdams ngag ltar na/
NK061(ku)001:2968: gzhung rgyas pa dang sbyar te bsdu ba dang /
NK061(ku)001:2969: theg pa rim pa dgu dang sbyar te bsdu ba dang /
NK061(ku)001:2970: dkyil 'khor bdun dang sbyar te bsdu ba dang /
NK061(ku)001:2971: bshad tshul gsum gyis ston no //
NK061(ku)001:2972: de yang e ma zhes pas ngam pa'i tshig ste/
NK061(ku)001:2973: rangs te yon tan la ngam pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:2974: ma rangs te skyon la ngam pa gnyis las/
NK061(ku)001:2976: de yang spyi dang bye brag gnyis las/
NK061(ku)001:2977: spyir ni e zhes pas gzhung rgyas pa dang sbyar te bsdu ba la ngam/
NK061(ku)001:2978: e ma zhes pas theg pa rim pa dgu'i don dang sbyar te bsdu ba la ngam/
NK061(ku)001:2979: e ma ho zhes pas dkyil 'khor bdun gyi don dang sbyar te bsdu ba la ngam pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2980: bye brag tu gzhung rgyas pa dang sbyar te bsdu ba ltar bshad na/
NK061(ku)001:2981: e zhes pas ston pa phun sum tshogs pa la ngam/
NK061(ku)001:2982: e ma zhes pas gnas phun sum tshogs pa la ngam/
NK061(ku)001:2983: e ma ho zhes pas 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la ngam pa'o //
NK061(ku)001:2984: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid ces pas sems nyid lhun gyis grub pa'i de bzhin nyid de/
NK061(ku)001:2985: mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings nyid du ye nas gnas pa/
NK061(ku)001:2986: gang du sdud na 'dir sdud la/
NK061(ku)001:2987: gang sdud na gnas kyi rang bzhin nam gzhi'i 'og min gsum bstan pa sdud de/
NK061(ku)001:2989: 'og min gyi rgya phyogs bcu phyi dang nang med pa zhes pa de sdud par gda'/
NK061(ku)001:2991: de yang don gong ma de yid byed pa po
NK061(ku)001:2992: rang byung gi ye shes kyis rtogs par mnga' mdzad
NK061(ku)001:2993: cing dbang sgyur ba/ gang du sdud na 'dir sdud la/
NK061(ku)001:2994: gang sdud na ston pa'i ngo bo dang 'chad pa'i
NK061(ku)001:2995: skyes bu mtshan thun mong du bstan pa'i gzhung tshig
NK061(ku)001:2996: rnams sdud de/ gang zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:2997: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa dbu gsum dang ldan pa/
NK061(ku)001:2998: zhes pa de rnams sdud par gda'/
NK061(ku)001:2999: ye shes dkyil 'khor thugs rje'i ngang //
NK061(ku)001:3000: zhes pas de yang rtogs pa'i rig pa nyid ye shes lngar gsal ba'i bye brag rnams las/
NK061(ku)001:3001: 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba/
NK061(ku)001:3002: dus gsum gyi chos kun dang rgya ma chad par thugs rje chen po'i ngang gis 'brel ba/
NK061(ku)001:3004: gang sdud na ston pa'i rang bzhin bdun bstan pa sdud de/
NK061(ku)001:3006: de bzhin gshegs pa rang bzhin te/
NK061(ku)001:3007: zhes pa de sdud par gda'/
NK061(ku)001:3008: rang snang ba nyid ces pas de rtogs pa'i rig
NK061(ku)001:3009: pa la 'bras bu sku dang ye shes thams cad
NK061(ku)001:3010: rdzogs pa nyid kyi rtsal ma 'gags par rang snang
NK061(ku)001:3011: ba nyid gru bzhi glo 'bur dbyibs dang kha dog
NK061(ku)001:3014: gang sdud na gnas kyi ngo bo bstan pa'i gzhung tshig rnams sdud de/
NK061(ku)001:3016: gzhi tshad med pa rgyan bsam gyis mi khyab par klubs pa/
NK061(ku)001:3017: zhes pa rnams sdud par gda'/
NK061(ku)001:3018: ting 'dzin zhes pas stong pa nyid la sogs pa
NK061(ku)001:3019: rnam par thar pa'i ting nge 'dzin bzhi'i sgo nas
NK061(ku)001:3020: 'jug pa/ gang du sdud na 'dir sdud/
NK061(ku)001:3021: gang sdud na sgo'i don bstan pa sdud de/
NK061(ku)001:3023: rnam par thar ba sgo khyud can/
NK061(ku)001:3024: zhes pa de sdud pa gda'/
NK061(ku)001:3026: theg pa brgyad kyi sgo nas bgrod pa'i don mtshon dgos pa'i phyiir te/
NK061(ku)001:3027: de'i gzugs brnyan rta babs brgyad du snang ba/
NK061(ku)001:3029: gang sdud na rta babs kyi don sdud de/
NK061(ku)001:3032: zhes pa de sdud par gda'/
NK061(ku)001:3033: sgyu ma zhes pas rtogs pa'i rig pa sgyu ma nyid/
NK061(ku)001:3034: stobs la sogs pa 'bras bu'i chos su snang ba seng ge la sogs pa lngar sgom pa ste/
NK061(ku)001:3036: gang sdud na sems can gyi gdan sdud de/
NK061(ku)001:3038: mi 'jigs pa nam mkha' lding gi khri dang /
NK061(ku)001:3039: zhes pa de sdud par gda'/
NK061(ku)001:3040: rnam dag ces pas thams cad rang rig pas spyad
NK061(ku)001:3041: kyang nyes pa'i skyon gyis mi gos pas rnam par
NK061(ku)001:3042: dag pa/ gang du sdud na 'dir sdud/
NK061(ku)001:3043: gang sdud na pad+ma'i gdan sdud de/
NK061(ku)001:3045: gos pa med pa pad+ma zhes pa de sdud par gda'/
NK061(ku)001:3047: zhes pas ma skyes pa'i ye shes nyid thabs dang
NK061(ku)001:3048: shes rab tu gsal bas cir yang mi 'gag par
NK061(ku)001:3049: rang snang ba/ gang du sdud na 'dir sdud/
NK061(ku)001:3050: gang sdud na nyi zla'i gdan sdud de/
NK061(ku)001:3052: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK061(ku)001:3053: zhes pa de sdu par gda'/
NK061(ku)001:3054: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin las zhes pas sku de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
NK061(ku)001:3058: phrin las las kyi rigs te/
NK061(ku)001:3059: phung po'ang 'byung ba kar dag pas rigs lnga yab yum du gsal ba/
NK061(ku)001:3061: gang sdud na sku mdog dang khyab pa'i tshad ma
NK061(ku)001:3062: gtogs pa'i rang bzhin gnyis med kyi 'khor rigs lnga
NK061(ku)001:3063: yab yum sdud de/ gang zhe na/
NK061(ku)001:3064: bcom ldan 'das 'du byed kyi rgyal po dang /
NK061(ku)001:3066: btsun mo la sogs pa zhes pa rnams sdud par gda'/
NK061(ku)001:3067: sel med pa yi zhes pas/
NK061(ku)001:3068: phung po dang 'byung bas ril sdud pa thams cad
